column68: The Mini Tracer is the perfect art projector for artist and crafter. This new compact and portable art projector makes it fun and easy to project and enlarge up to 8 times your designs, patterns, lettering, sketches - even small objects. Simply place the image or object under the projector, turn on the switch, focus, and project in full colour onto a wall, canvas, paper, fabric or virtually any vertical surface. Then trace, paint and finish as desired. The Mini Tracer will help you to be more creative and have more fun! Specifications: Copy size: 9cm x 9cm (3 1/2” x 3 1/2”). Projection range: 4 to 8 times enlargement. Electrical: 23Ov and 115 v. Net Weight: 9kg (2lbs.). Illumination: 100 Watts Maximum. Fan cooled, thermally protected.

column68: Artograph, the leading manufacturer of projectors since 1947, presents the Tracer, a quality projector at an unprecedented price. It requires no assembly. Simply place the projector on top of the design, pattern or photograph, push the “on” button, and the image is projected and enlarged instantly with clarity and in full colour for your drawing pleasure. Trace your way from patterns and designs with enjoyment toward the fun of filling in with colour and creativity. Enlarges up to 10 times. Lightweight and portable. Accurate horizontal projection. Projection of small 3-D items. Oversized images in sections. Full colour or black and white images. Silent operation. UL listed. Specifications: copy size: 5” x 5” (127mm x 127mm), illumination: up to 100 watts maximum, lens: 200mm optical glass, horizontal range: 2-10X, electrical: 115v, 9 amps - 220v available, net weight: 3Ibs.(1.36kg). Warranty: 1 year.

column68: The Super Prism professional quality projector offers increased performance and special features to make scaling art-work and designs faster and easier than ever before. Features 500 watts of photo quality lighting for a whiter and brighter image. A generous 7”x 7” glass covered copy area makes for easy placement of large copy books, or small 3-D objects. New magnetic latches and an arching spring clip keeps copy securely in place. A dual channel cooling system and a safety thermal overload circuit protects copy from overheating. The Prism projectors will help you get to the creative part faster. Features a 3 element, colour corrected lens for extra sharp images and increased brightness. Ideal for working from a variety of more challenging originals like photographs, half-tones and highly detailed drawings. Enlarges originals from 3 to 20 times. Specifications: copy size 7” x 7” (17.8cm x 17.8cm), illumination 2/250 watt photo lamps, horizontal range is 300% to 2000%, electrical 110V - 3.3 amps, net weight is 9Ibs. (18.2kg). Warranty 5 years.

column68: Watermark Whitecore is a high quality, acid free matboard that has been manufactured to internationally recognised standards for the permanence of paper as specified for conservation framing. Watermark Whitecore’s facing papers and backing liner are acid free, made from pure neutral sized cellulose, buffered with calcium carbonate (minimum 3% by weight). The crisp, clean, white core is made from high grade, fully bleached hardwood and softwood pulp, which is lignin free. It is buffered with calcium carbonate and has a pH of 7.7 to 8.3, which is acid free. The adhesive used is pure water-based PVA, containing no solvents and with a pH of 7.5, which is acid free. Watermark Whitecore is available in the most popular colours, each individually selected for their suitability for use in the unique Australian framing environment, and all of which are proven “top sellers”. Thickness is 1400ums, which is 4 ply.

column68: Alphamat Artcare is ideal for both conservation and general framing, including original works of art, limited-edition prints, photography, newsprint, historical documents, decorative art, posters and graphics, gallery and exhibit framing. Featuring the latest colours, Alphamat has a pure solid white core for clean, consistent bevels, making it ideal for creative cuts. Fade and bleed-resistant with guaranteed colour consistency. 100% Non-Acidic: Alphamat features an alkaline sizing. Plus Alphamat is buffered with calcium carbonate to protect against acidic elements in the environment and maintain an alkaline pH. Alphamat Artcare Vellums: This offers a complete range of smooth surfaced, specially sized neutrals, ideal for French matting, washlines and other decorative surface treatments.
